<LP>
   SALT LAKE CITY -- Evans &amp; Sutherland Computer Corp. said
it was selected to design and build visual systems for the
Air Force Tanker/Transport Training System. The contract,
valued at more than $20 million, covers 11 visual systems for
flight-training simulators.
   Evans &amp; Sutherland makes interactive computer systems for
engineering and scientific applications.
